ecule $\\lambda_{d3He}=192(3)\\cdot 10^6 s^{-1}$ and the\nprobability of the fast muon transfer from the excited to the ground state of\nthe $\\mu\\;d$ atom $q_{1S}=0.80(3)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jan 2020 17:33:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 13 Feb 2021 04:34:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 17 Jun 2021 04:09:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-18"}
