 $K_{O} \\sim 5$) whatever is the independent variable. We\nalso verified that our bolometric corrections correctly predict the AGN\nbolometric luminosity functions. According to this analysis, our bolometric\ncorrections can be applied to the whole AGN population in a wide range of\nluminosity and redshift.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jan 2020 18:59:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-22"}
