imilar adaptive smoothing is implemented on the Lagrangian\nPT fields to identify haloes and is combined with a spherical halo prescription\nto account for post-collapse dynamics. Again, a suppression is found in the\ncoupling between small- and large-scale modes and the agreement with\nsimulations is improved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jan 2020 15:43:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Sep 2020 16:35:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-30"}
